Install Ubuntu as normal
Additional software or packages
  |--Sublime Text 3
  |  |--Get the Sublime security key:
  |     |--$ wget -qO - https://download.sublimetext.com/sublimehq-pub.gpg | sudo apt-key add -
  |  |--$ sudo apt-get 
  |
  |--G++
  |  |--$ sudo apt install g++
  |
  |--Valgrind
     |--$ sudo apt install valgrind
